QuestData.Title: I Never Forget a Face
QuestData.Description: You have discovered a partially digested head. Lord Godfrey perks up when he sees it. Perhaps you should give it to him.
QuestData.LogDescription: Give the Partially Digested Head to Lord Godfrey in Silverpine Forest.
QuestData.RewardText: I know that face, $n. This head belongs to a former Gilnean known as Sean Dempsey. He was imprisoned with Crowley before the great outbreak.$B$BI wonder if it would be possible to put him back together. The rest of him must be in the belly of these crocolisks.
